Media
Light novel
Written by Mugi Mameta, Dinners with My Darling: How the Former Monster King Ate Her Way to Happiness was initially serialized on Shōsetsuka ni Narō from April 3, 2022 to October 5, 2023. It was later acquired by Futabasha who began publishing the series under their M Novels f light novel imprint on October 7, 2022. Six volumes have been released as of November 10, 2025.
In December 2024, Cross Infinite World announced that they had licensed the series for digital-only English publication.
