Manga
A manga adaptation illustrated by Toi Ishino began serialization on Futabasha's Gaugau Monster website on January 11, 2023. The manga's chapters have been collected into six tankōbon volumes as of November 2025.
The manga adaptation is published in English on NTT Solmare's MangaPlaza website.
